node.text: Last night on @entertainmenttonight 📺 we talked about my recovery after my hand injury, the new season of Buddy Vs. Duff on @foodnetwork and some cake decorating @carlosbakery with quite the talent @rachelsmithtv #buddyvsduff #cakeboss #americanacake #olympics2021 #summerolympics @discoveryplus

node.title: What a blast co-host with @rachelsmithtv last night @entertainmenttonight

node.text: Watch me and #TeamBuddy build cakes inspired by an African safari in just two days before presenting them to the toughest judges yet, a panel of 50 talented cake artists from across America. Watch tonight, DVR or stream @discoveryplus 📺

node.text:
I recently had the pleasure of spending some time in the kitchen with @gigihadid The August cover star of @harpersbazaarus To go over some cake decorating techniques! Gigi really wins over my heart telling me about all of her favorite #CakeBoss moments!
.
Check it out and let me know what you guys think of my newest summer intern?!?

node.title: Spending a little time in the kitchen with the #iconic @gigihadid

node.text:
Hey guys, bring Mom to @tgif for a Mother’s Day celebration she’ll be sure to enjoy! 
.
Our new @carlosbakery Cookies and Cream Tsunami Cake is now available to order at your neighborhood @tgifridays
.
Enjoy it to-go and have some fun at home! Tag me and @carlosbakery with your Tsunami experience for a chance to receive some @carlosbakery sweets delivered to your door! 
.
#tsunamicake #mothersday #mothersday2021 #cookiesandcream #cookiesandcreamcake

Feel the magic of Christmas with #BuddyVsChristmas SHARE if you’ll be watching with me! 
.

.
It’s a Christmas Extravaganza you won’t want to miss!

node.text: Coffee lovers, I’ve got a real treat for you! I took inspiration from the delicious desserts and pastries @carlosbakery and put them into my newest line of k-cup coffee! They’re only available online to be delivered right to your doorstep so head over to Carlosbakery.com/coffee or my stories and swipe up for the link ☕️ #coffeelover #coffeetime #coffeegram #coffeelife #coffeelife

node.text:
Cohosting with @rachelsmithtv last night on @entertainmenttonight head over to my IGTV for the full video! We talk about my hand recovery, new season of #BuddyVsDuff @foodnetwork and decorate our summer favorite @carlosbakery Americana cake 🇺🇸 
.
Repost from @rachelsmithtv
•
Move over Gigi Hadid— I think I may be the Cake Boss’ new biggest fan! 🤩 Trying my hand at cake decorating with my guest co-host Buddy Valastro. (TRYING being the key word!) Buddy, it’s a wonder I’m not STILL decorating that cake. 🐢😳😂 An update from the Cake Boss himself on his recovery after his hand was impaled in a freak accident at his home bowling alley, and he teases what’s to come on Buddy vs Duff. Thank you, Buddy, for being as sweet as your delicious cakes! ☺️🙌🏽🎂 #cakeboss #carlosbakery #sweettooth #baking

node.text: Last night on @entertainmenttonight 📺 we talked about my recovery after my hand injury, the new season of Buddy Vs. Duff on @foodnetwork and some cake decorating @carlosbakery with quite the talent @rachelsmithtv #buddyvsduff #cakeboss #americanacake #olympics2021 #summerolympics @discoveryplus
What did you guys think of last nights episode of #buddyvsduff 🤔#teambuddy had a blast creating these life size safari themed cake animals! 🦏 🐊 🦛 #cakesofinstagram #cakeart #cakedesign #cakeboss
